*Isti* dan je bila utrošena cela suma novca. (The same day the whole amount of money was spent.)

*Istom* se prilikom dogodilo nešto neočekivano. (At the same time something unexpected happened.)

On je iste* večeri završio posao. (He finished the job that same evening.)

*Istog* dana počeli su da gradi novi most. (They started to build a new bridge on the same day.)

*Ista* se stvar ponovila narednih dana. (The same thing repeated the following days.)